         <abstract>
           <p>The attribution of the hymn to John the Evangelist is based on <bibl><ptr target="bm:Chaine1913Rep"></ptr></bibl>. However,
           according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:Wright1877BM"></ptr></bibl> it is addressed to John the Baptist, whereas
         <bibl><ptr target="bm:EMML7"></ptr><citedRange unit="page">104-105</citedRange></bibl> ascribes it to emperor <persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs I</persName>.</p>
